{"tid":2211750,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"(全港獨家)亞洲手機熱爆新GAME榜(2020AUG)","createTime":"2020-09-21T10:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T02:38:58.000Z","uid":345840,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"059df47679d503b6cfad864d66ed7d1f20d975ac","tid":2211750,"uid":345840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:12:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HkZb0R-ib2E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHkZb0R-ib2E&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZop1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=a2a65d1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HkZb0R-ib2E</a><br />\n<br />\n我又整左8月份手遊最TOP下載排行榜啦<br />\n上次有人屌點解講黎講都係大陸GAME<br />\n其實係因為香港個市場本身就多大陸GAME多人玩<br />\n為左避免呢個情況<br />\n今次專登做闊D做哂日本、韓國、台灣、香港同泰國<br />\n希望大家會鍾意睇啦"},{"pid":"1977197f910dfe529c288dfd1c6af9856686cf9f","tid":2211750,"uid":155374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x2iwADf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2iwADf.png&h=1050cf91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H1QKVDf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH1QKVDf.png&h=f36be45b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nWJDZ4V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnWJDZ4V.png&h=e9fb1fa4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6JwFtYg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6JwFtYg.png&h=69b784f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gGRmXRC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgGRmXRC.png&h=1bb87b32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tQu6KX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tQu6KX.png&h=f3f56012&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUG2Hih.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUG2Hih.png&h=e55672c9&s=